# TASK 05 - Flatten Current Repo (XML)

## Goal
Create a single XML artifact for the active repo for machine-focused workflows.

## Output (authoritative)
- ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts/codebase.xml

## Preconditions
- TASK 03 succeeded
- project_context available

## Steps
1. mkdir -p ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts
2. node bin/cli.js \
   --config config/flattener.config.json \
   --root . \
   --format xml \
   --out ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts/codebase.xml
3. Record artifact path in the turn manifest if present.
